# data/

Datasets are hosted on Zenodo, not stored in this repository, to keep the
codebase lightweight and to give the data a citable, versioned DOI.

## Expected structure

Scripts in `scripts/` read from and write to this structure. Download
the files listed below from Zenodo and place them accordingly before
running any script.

```
data/
├── raw/
│   ├── YahooFinance_25coins_2017_2025.csv
│   └── ALL_coins_daily_multi_exchange_v5.csv
└── processed/
    ├── YahooFinance_dataset_learning_v2.csv
    ├── dataset_features.csv                 (generated by scripts/multiexchange/01_...)
    └── dataset_learning_v2.csv              (generated by scripts/multiexchange/03_...)
```

Files under `processed/` for the multi-exchange pipeline are generated
locally by running the scripts in order (see
`scripts/multiexchange/README.md`) — they do not need to be downloaded
separately, only the `raw/` file does.

## Zenodo records

| Dataset | DOI | Contents |
|---|---|---|
| Yahoo Finance benchmark | 10.5281/zenodo.21377192 | `YahooFinance_dataset_learning_v2.csv` + documentation |
| Multi-exchange benchmark | [ADD DOI] | `ALL_coins_daily_multi_exchange_v5.csv` (raw) |
| YoBit personal trading history | [ADD DOI] | Personal trading records used for Level 4 validation |

## Column definitions

See `data/FEATURES.md` for the full feature dictionary across all three
data sources (naming differs between the Yahoo Finance and multi-exchange
pipelines — this file maps equivalent features across both).

## Note

`data/raw/` and `data/processed/` are excluded from version control via
`.gitignore`. Do not commit CSV files to this repository directly.
